sequenceDiagram
  actor User
  participant FE as React UI
  participant BE as FastAPI
  participant Model as YOLOS Model
  participant DB as SQLite

  User->>FE: Upload gambar
  FE->>BE: POST /predict (image)
  BE->>Model: Jalankan inferensi
  Model-->>BE: boxes + scores + labels
  BE->>DB: Simpan log prediksi (opsional)
  BE-->>FE: JSON hasil deteksi
  FE-->>User: Tampilkan bbox + label + confidence
